#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:60
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:286
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:386
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:486
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:588
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:690
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:792
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:955
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:1057
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:1152
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:1247
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:1344
msgid ""
"Instead of showing a CAPTCHA challenge, reCAPTCHA v3 returns a score so you "
"can choose the most appropriate action for your website. The score is based "
"on interactions with your site and enables you to take an appropriate "
"action for your site. reCaptcha will rank traffic and interactions based on "
"a score of 0.0 to 1.0, with a 1.0 being a good interaction and scores "
"closer to 0.0 indicating a good likelihood that the traffic was generated "
"by bots"
msgstr ""

#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:80
msgid "Note :- "
msgstr ""

#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:118
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:1400
msgid ""
"reCaptcha V3 does not show any challenge like I am not robot etc. reCaptcha "
"V3 uses a behind-the-scenes scoring system to detect abusive traffic, and "
"lets you decide the minimum passing score. Please note that there is no "
"user interaction shown in reRecapcha V3 meaning that no recaptcha challenge "
"is shown to solve."
msgstr ""

